com.googlecode.aviator.asm.tree

类 FieldInsnNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.aviator.asm.tree.AbstractInsnNode
      • com.googlecode.aviator.asm.tree.FieldInsnNode

  • public class FieldInsnNode
extends AbstractInsnNode
    A node that represents a field instruction. A field instruction is an instruction that loads or stores the value of a field of an object.
    作者:
    Eric Bruneton

      The internal name of the field's owner class (see getInternalName).

    • 构造器详细资料

      • FieldInsnNode

        public FieldInsnNode(int opcode,
             String owner,
             String name,
             String desc)
        Constructs a new FieldInsnNode.
        参数:
        opcode - the opcode of the type instruction to be constructed. This opcode must be GETSTATIC, PUTSTATIC, GETFIELD or PUTFIELD.
        owner - the internal name of the field's owner class (see getInternalName).
        name - the field's name.
        desc - the field's descriptor (see Type).
